.DT
forwards
Discworld creator help
forwards

.SH Name
.SI 5
forwards - Shows how many bugs someone has forwarded
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
forwards <player name>
forwards all
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Counts up the numbers of bugs that someone has forwarded using information
generated from the SQL bug database.
If the all keyword is
used then the bug reports will be listed in order of who has forwarded the
most to who has forwarded the least.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> forwards all
> forwards pinkfish
.EI

.SH See Also
.SP 5 5
fixed, bugreps, denied
.EP
